<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{١٧٠}</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{وإذا قيل لهم}</span>؛ <span class="c3">{قيل}</span> مبني<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>